        public static PsiType getOptionalElementType(PsiType type)
        Unwraps an Optional, OptionalInt, OptionalLong or OptionalDouble returning its element type
        Parameters:
        type - a type representing optional (e.g. Optional<String> or OptionalInt)
        Returns:
        an element type (e.g. String or int). Returns null if the supplied type is not an optional type or its a raw java.util.Optional.
